Arguments: [A configuration file]
External functions: All functionality must be implemented in C++ 98.
execve, pipe, strerror, gai_strerror, errno, dup, dup2, fork, socketpair, htons, htonl, ntohs, ntohl,
select, poll, epoll (epoll_create, epoll_ctl, epoll_wait), kqueue (kqueue, kevent), socket,
accept, listen, send, recv, chdir, bind, connect, getaddrinfo, freeaddrinfo, setsockopt, getsockname,
